                    <p><span>Our esteemed faculty and programs are nationally and internationally recognized for excellence and creativity, providing a foundation for a rigorous academic experience while maintaining our focus on the individual student. </span></p>
<p><span>We offer 60 major and 55 minor undergraduate degrees and programs.For graduate students, we have 39 master's degree programs, one education doctorate, on juris doctorate, one doctorate of juridical science and 10 credential/authorization programs. Our esteemed faculty includes Nobel Prize winners and Pulitzer Price winners, among many other distinctions. We are a top producer of U.S. Fulbright Students.</span></p>
