        	<div class="header__info__heading">Change Starts Here</div>
          	<p><span>Research and creative work is integral to the development of our students. Starting on the first day of their undergraduate experience, students have unprecedented access to faculty-mentored research programs. LMU faculty received $5.4 million in sponsored projects last year, ranging from scientific research to artistic endeavors.</span></p>
