        <div class="header__info__content">
        	<div class="header__info__heading">Investing in You</div>
          <p>We prepare our students to thrive as global citizens, thought leaders, professionals, and well-rounded men and women for others. We take pride in developing our students into alumni who are ethical business leaders, artists, and scholars. Discerning a student's vocation develops them into persons alive to possibilities, creative storytellers, and engineers of socially responsible global change. </p>
<p>Our successful students and alumni provide evidence of the return on investment an LMU education provides. In addition to exploring what they are called to do, LMU graduates lead lives of meaning and purpose, which translates into personal fulfillment, financial independence, and professional achievement. The LMU alumni network is engaged and global with more than 50,000 living undergraduate alumni, 19,000 graduate alumni and 17,000 law school alumni.</p>
